---
title: Cheesy Pumpkin Fusilli & Sage-Walnut Crumb with Pear & Rocket Salad
description: The star of this pasta night is the moreish creamy sauce, with roasted butternut pumpkin stirred through, it’ll melt in your mouth
upon first bite. Topped off with a sage-infused walnut crumb, your senses will be in for a very special treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-pumpkin-fusilli-sage-walnut-crumb-fbd66c27.jpg
